gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Nuggets 122, Nets 117
gameRecap.excerpt: The Nuggets defeated the Nets, 122-117. Jamal Murray recorded a new season-high 32 points, with nine assists and five rebounds for the Nuggets, while Nikola Jokic added 31 points, 11 rebounds, and seven assists in the victory. Cam Thomas tallied 23 points and two assists for the Nets in the losing effort. The Nuggets improve to 20-10 in the regular season, while the Nets fall to 13-15.
